"currently using 490 kbytes, the user can only allocate an additional 10 "
"kbytes.  Attempting to allocate an additional 11 kbytes will fail."
msgstr ""
"硬性限制是一种不能越过的限制。 一旦用户达到了系统指定的硬性限制， 他就无法在"
