#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/disks/_index.adoc:2287
msgid ""
"Configuration of HAST is done using [.filename]#/etc/hast.conf#.  This file "
"should be identical on both nodes.  The simplest configuration is:"
